1. Šta se *dešava*? (What's happening?)
2. *Dešava* se da mi nedostaješ. (It happens that I miss you.)
3. Kada se to *dešava*? (When does that happen?)
4. Ništa se ne *dešava*. (Nothing is happening.)
5. Nije mi se *dešavalo* da se tako osećam. (It hadn't happened to me to feel that way before.)
6. To mi se *dešavalo* u prošlosti. (That used to happen to me in the past.)
7. Nema razloga da se tako nešto *dešava*. (There's no reason for something like that to happen.)
8. Šta će se *dešavati* u budućnosti? (What will happen in the future?)
9. Molim te da se to ne *dešava* opet. (Please, don't let that happen again.)
10. Nekada se *dešavalo* da zaboravim. (It used to happen to me that I forget.)